# Experiment Helper Privacy Policy

Effective Date: June 8, 2026

Experiment Helper is a laboratory utility app for iOS and macOS that provides calculators and lookup tools for molecular biology, biochemistry, and chemical biology workflows.

## Overview

Experiment Helper does not collect, store, sell, or share personal information.

The app does not require an account. The app does not use advertising. The app does not use third-party analytics. The app does not track users across apps or websites.

## Data Collection

Experiment Helper does not collect data from users.

Most calculations are performed locally on the user’s device. These include, but are not limited to:

- Protein property calculations
- DNA and RNA translation
- Dilution calculations
- Dilution factor calculations
- Transfection calculations
- Cell seeding calculations

Inputs entered for these local calculations are processed on the device and are not sent to the developer.

## Third-Party Lookup Services

Some features use user-initiated network requests to public scientific databases.

### UniProt

When a user enters a UniProt accession, Experiment Helper sends that accession to UniProt to retrieve protein sequence information.

### PubChem

When a user enters a CAS number or compound identifier, Experiment Helper sends that query to PubChem to retrieve compound information.

Experiment Helper does not operate UniProt or PubChem and does not control their privacy practices. Users should refer to UniProt and PubChem for information about their respective data practices.

## Tracking

Experiment Helper does not track users across apps or websites.

## Advertising

Experiment Helper does not display advertising.

## Analytics

Experiment Helper does not use third-party analytics services.

## Accounts

Experiment Helper does not require users to create an account or sign in.

## Children’s Privacy

Experiment Helper is intended as a general laboratory and educational utility. The app does not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.

